title: [Silken Mist, Deck]
description: Several sturdy clamps have been set into the deck to allow deep sea fishing from this spot, and based on how thick and solid the devices are, the sealife must put up quite a fight.  Two large buckets have been secured on the deck to hold any of the catches that lucky anglers might make.
room.location: Silken Mist on Four Winds Isle
